</ul>

<ul class="wikiUnorderedList">
<li class="wikiUnorderedListItem"> <a href="http://community.jboss.org/people/jharting" target="" class="regularLink">Jozef Hartinger</a> moved to Weld team to work on <a href="http://community.jboss.org/wiki/Weld2ImplementationPlan" target="" class="regularLink">Weld 2.0 (CDI 1.1 impl)</a>
</li>
</ul>


<br>

<p class="wikiPara">
Onward to Weld 1.2 and 2.0!!
